item.title: MAN
item.description:
light is dark

The ideology behind this expression is that only through darkness can the necessity is known else it would be too much to take in .

Derrick Rose is one of the NBA players who had been fatally injured during his prime time . This situation did bring darkness into his life and made Derrick go on a tough quest in the search of light.

He finally made it , scoring his career highest of 50 points in a single game.

Now he knows his true light source
